---
const { frontmatter } = Astro.props;
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
  <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-V4YWW8GMPB"></script>
  <script is:inline>
    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
    function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
    gtag('js', new Date());
    gtag('config', 'G-V4YWW8GMPB');
  </script>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{frontmatter.title} - AI実践ラボ</title>
  <meta name="description" content={frontmatter.description}>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/article.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": frontmatter.title,
    "author": {"@type": "Person", "name": "Tokimo"},
    "publisher": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "AI実践ラボ"},
    "datePublished": frontmatter.date,
  })} />
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header-inner">
        <a href="/" class="logo">
          <span class="logo-icon">🤖</span>
          <span class="logo-text">AI実践ラボ</span>
        </a>
        <nav class="main-nav">
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/#tools">ツール比較</a></li>
            <li><a href="/#howto">使い方ガイド</a></li>
            <li><a href="/#reviews">レビュー</a></li>
            <li><a href="/#sidejob">AI副業</a></li>
          </ul>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="article-main">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="article-layout">
        <article class="article-body">
          <nav class="breadcrumb">
            <a href="/">ホーム</a> &gt;
            <a href="/#tools">{frontmatter.category}</a> &gt;
            <span>{frontmatter.title}</span>
          </nav>

          <div class="article-header">
            <span class="article-category">{frontmatter.category}</span>
            <span class="article-date">{frontmatter.date}</span>
          </div>

          <h1>{frontmatter.title}</h1>

          {frontmatter.rating && (
            <div class="article-info-box">
              {frontmatter.rating && <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">総合評価</span><span class="info-value">{frontmatter.rating}</span></div>}
              {frontmatter.price && <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">料金</span><span class="info-value">{frontmatter.price}</span></div>}
              {frontmatter.difficulty && <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">難易度</span><span class="info-value">{frontmatter.difficulty}</span></div>}
              {frontmatter.target && <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">こんな人向け</span><span class="info-value">{frontmatter.target}</span></div>}
            </div>
          )}

          <slot />

          <div class="affiliate-box">
            <a href="https://claude.ai/" class="btn btn-primary btn-large" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              Claude 公式サイトで始める →
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="callout">
            <div class="callout-icon">🖥️</div>
            <div class="callout-content">
              <strong>サイト公開にはレンタルサーバーが必要</strong><br>
              Claude Codeで作ったサイトを公開するなら、高速・安定のレンタルサーバーがおすすめ。ConoHa WINGなら月額660円〜、独自ドメイン永久無料。<br>
              <a href="https://px.a8.net/svt/ejp?a8mat=4B1HTI+941VVE+50+5SIFHE" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">ConoHa WING 公式サイトはこちら →</a>
              <img src="https://www17.a8.net/0.gif?a8mat=4B1HTI+941VVE+50+5SIFHE" alt="" width="1" height="1" style="border:none;">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="callout">
            <div class="callout-icon">📚</div>
            <div class="callout-content">
              <strong>AI・プログラミング関連の書籍・機材を探すなら</strong><br>
              <a href="https://rpx.a8.net/svt/ejp?a8mat=3TNNXL+5E3CRE+2HOM+6C1VM&rakuten=y&a8ejpredirect=http%3A%2F%2Fhb.afl.rakuten.co.jp%2Fhgc%2F0ea62065.34400275.0ea62066.204f04c0%2Fa23121174074_3TNNXL_5E3CRE_2HOM_6C1VM%3Fpc%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.rakuten.co.jp%252F%26m%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fm.rakuten.co.jp%252F" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">楽天で AI関連アイテムを探す →</a>
              <img border="0" width="1" height="1" src="https://www11.a8.net/0.gif?a8mat=3TNNXL+5E3CRE+2HOM+6C1VM" alt="" style="border:none;">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="callout">
            <div class="callout-icon">🎓</div>
            <div class="callout-content">
              <strong>プログラミングの基礎も学びたい方へ</strong><br>
              <a href="https://px.a8.net/svt/ejp?a8mat=4B1HTI+95U6OQ+4K3S+5YJRM" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">SkillHacks(スキルハックス) を見る →</a>
              <img border="0" width="1" height="1" src="https://www17.a8.net/0.gif?a8mat=4B1HTI+95U6OQ+4K3S+5YJRM" alt="" style="border:none;">
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <aside class="sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-widget author-widget">
            <h3>この記事を書いた人</h3>
            <div class="author-info">
              <div class="author-name">Tokimo</div>
              <p class="author-desc">非エンジニアのClaude Code実践者。プログラミング経験ゼロからAIツールを使いこなし、業務自動化を実現。</p>
              <a href="https://x.com/Tokimo2026" class="author-link" target="_blank">@Tokimo2026</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="sidebar-widget cta-widget">
            <h3>Xで最新情報を発信中</h3>
            <p>Claude Codeの実践ノウハウを毎日投稿</p>
            <a href="https://x.com/Tokimo2026" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">フォローする</a>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2026 AI実践ラボ by Tokimo. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
